{"tid":279250,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"癲狗系列 - 香蒜辣椒火腿炒意粉","createTime":"2017-06-11T06:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-14T04:28:25.000Z","uid":74981,"like":24,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ab1669edf9f29967e1346681dc3987a1a208a42","tid":279250,"uid":74981,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s16.postimg.org/dgf37zq4l/20170611_133001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs16.postimg.org%2Fdgf37zq4l%2F20170611_133001.jpg&h=249bbf86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>影片如下:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kqDZWRpHmJY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkqDZWRpHmJY&d=ejsX3kHsxERRDkFiosH%2B%2BG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=73367fac\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kqDZWRpHmJY</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>材料:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 意粉1人粉量<br />\n<br />\n2. 蒜蓉2茶匙<br />\n<br />\n3. 辣椒2隻切碎<br />\n<br />\n4. 火腿絲少許<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>做法:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 開獲落水, 油, 鹽煮滾, 落意粉煮約7分半鐘 (隻隻牌子唔同), 意粉芯開始變淋, 撈起隔水.<br />\n<br />\n2. 洗獲, 大火燒紅獲, 落油, 轉中小火, 先落火腿, 再落辣椒, 轉細火再落蒜蓉爆, 唔好俾D蒜蓉變黃, 然後落意炒快炒一陣, 完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a629e0a77b8efcb8266f86e9d2b171edc9327c","tid":279250,"uid":74981,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:23:49.000Z","msg":"意粉芯開始變淋其實我表達得唔好，應該話意粉芯林左唔好超過9成左右就撈起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2614c8ece4ccaf47f4ed89b7c87e50b03f35fa9b","tid":279250,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:23:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00388b96721c9c4b5e101c2165845747be9c7603","tid":279250,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:24:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48314f29e8094a6fdbd013310a17f650363a2f77","tid":279250,"uid":74981,"like":6,"dislike":1,"scor